query:
SELECT 
  i.id,
  i.tenantId,
  wl.code AS endereco,
  p.name AS produto,
  p.sku AS refProduto,
  i.batch AS lote,
  i.quantity AS quantidadeDisponivel,
  i.status,
  i.expiryDate AS validade
FROM inventory i
JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id
JOIN products p ON i.productId = p.id
WHERE i.tenantId = 1
ORDER BY wl.code, p.sku, i.batch
LIMIT 20;
